# TexTemplate

LaTeX template for general document use.

Requires xelatex, Ruby, RubyGems, and the Bundler gem.  You may substitute another 

Setup:

  $ gem install bundler
  $ bundle install

Rake tasks:

  $ rake clean
  $ rake 
  $ rake pdf
  $ rake TEX_FILENAME_MINUS_EXTENSION

Use Guard:

  $ bundle exec guard  # Automatically compile tex sources as they are updated

